  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Retro Dungeon Crawler!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/60b107e34924126598664e63a13e6d21.avif?t=1772361215\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Dungeon Slayer is a retro FPS dungeon crawler where you battle through procedurally generated dungeons filled with monsters. Wield swords, discover powerful upgrades, and fight for survival against waves of deadly creatures!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/4a6378182e23c6a1f18babb268a53b0e.webp?t=1772361215\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.poster.avif?t=1772361215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.webm?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.mp4?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Retro Dungeon Slayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro Dungeon Slayer is a retro-inspired FPS roguelike dungeon crawler with a pixelated, Minecraft-like aesthetic. Players explore procedurally generated dungeons, facing deadly creatures while choosing from a variety of weapons to survive. The game delivers fast-paced, action-packed combat with a nostalgic yet modern feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/b6cf22db840c18717a5601bf56f48c21.webp?t=1772361215\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.poster.avif?t=1772361215\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.webm?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.mp4?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run in Retro Dungeon Slayer is unique, requiring players to be strategic with their weapon choices and adapt to the ever-changing dungeon layouts. With over 10 enemy types and intense boss fights, players must stay sharp to survive. The focus on replayability, dynamic combat, and constant challenges makes each playthrough an exciting adventure.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Dungeon Slayer is a retro FPS dungeon crawler where you battle through procedurally generated dungeons filled with monsters. Wield swords, discover powerful upgrades, and fight for survival against waves of deadly creatures!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/4a6378182e23c6a1f18babb268a53b0e.webp?t=1772361215\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.poster.avif?t=1772361215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.webm?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.mp4?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Retro Dungeon Slayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro Dungeon Slayer is a retro-inspired FPS roguelike dungeon crawler with a pixelated, Minecraft-like aesthetic. Players explore procedurally generated dungeons, facing deadly creatures while choosing from a variety of weapons to survive. The game delivers fast-paced, action-packed combat with a nostalgic yet modern feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/b6cf22db840c18717a5601bf56f48c21.webp?t=1772361215\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.poster.avif?t=1772361215\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.webm?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.mp4?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run in Retro Dungeon Slayer is unique, requiring players to be strategic with their weapon choices and adapt to the ever-changing dungeon layouts. With over 10 enemy types and intense boss fights, players must stay sharp to survive. The focus on replayability, dynamic combat, and constant challenges makes each playthrough an exciting adventure.</p>",
